{"tid":2138969,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《上氣》復工開拍！那些「中國式」宮殿究竟代表著什麼呢？","createTime":"2020-08-04T03:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T10:02:57.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"410063c951afbccf62e0edd5eff1cba4bb3ad2d8","tid":2138969,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:42:51.000Z","msg":"漫威的《上氣與十環幫傳奇》（Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings）已準備好恢復拍攝。最新的影片展示了為了拍攝所搭建的中國式宮殿場景。<br />\n<br />\n《上氣》今年年初在澳大利亞開始拍攝 &nbsp;。但是新冠肺炎的大流行很快就讓拍攝工作停工了，導演德斯汀&middot;丹尼爾&middot;克雷頓（Destin Daniel Cretton）甚至去篩檢。雖然檢驗報告是陰性，但拍攝工作還是停了幾個月。在最近七月底時上氣又恢復拍攝了。<br />\n澳洲的7NEWS 分享了一些《上氣》的空拍畫面，從圖片中我們可以看到正在建造的中國式古老村莊，目前《上氣》的演員群已經陸續回到澳洲，並接受病毒檢測，而楊紫瓊也被目擊在上週於澳洲接受病毒檢測，這間接證實了楊紫瓊將會參與此片的演出。拍攝工作預計將在未來幾天內再次開始。以下是外景地的影片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0BJQlwrizzk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0BJQlwrizzk&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O3T1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=979f71bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0BJQlwrizzk</a>"},{"pid":"752fbe1a40a874d31f765670474622d5c1705fa0","tid":2138969,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159644309121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159644309121.jpg&h=c00e37ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159644310220.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159644310220.jpg&h=077bfe9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/geekbase/159644311440.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fgeekbase%2F159644311440.jpg&h=b8f12897&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03265dd08850c87c128bd64d24b4c8d6f60a4096","tid":2138969,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:00:13.000Z","msg"